dct_title_s: Geologic map of the Chounet Ranch quadrangle, Fresno County, California
dct_description_sm: by Thomas W. Dibblee, Jr. ; edited by John A. Minch.
Relief shown by contours and spot heights.
"Topographic base map from available USGS 7.5-minute quadrangle Chounet Ranch, CA 1956; photorevised 1971. AMS 1857 II NW - series V895."
Includes location map, index to adjacent 7.5 minute quadrangles, and index to sources of geology, most recent 1975.
